Turn Shoes into fashioned toys
2013-05-10 03:29:47 GMT
Ocean Sole flip-flop recycling company in Nairobi, Kenya is cleaning the East African country's beaches of used, washed-up flip-flops and the dirty pieces of rubber that were once cruising the Indian Ocean's currents are now being turned into colorful handmade giraffes, elephants and other toy animals.
